title: NOAA,  BP oil spill results in fishing ban in the Federally controlled waters of GOM, USA, May 04 2010
name: NOAA,  BP oil spill results in fishing ban in the Federally controlled waters of GOM, USA, May 04 2010
description:
NOAA has banned fishing in parts of the GOM near Louisiana, Mississippi and Alabama coastlines. The polyshape file shows the spatial extent of this ban.
